@page "/docs/architecture"

<PageTitle>Architecture - Tldraw.Blazor Docs</PageTitle>

<div class="docs-content">
    <h1>Architecture</h1>
    <p class="docs-lead">Tldraw.Blazor is organized into three layers: Core engine, SkiaSharp rendering, and Blazor UI.</p>

    <h2 id="layers">
        Project Layers
        <a class="docs-anchor" href="#layers">#</a>
    </h2>

    <CodeBlock Language="text" Code="Tldraw.Blazor.Core/           ← Pure C#, no UI dependencies
├── Editor/
│   ├── Camera.cs              ← Pan/Zoom/Transform
│   ├── Editor.cs              ← Central engine
│   ├── SelectionManager.cs    ← Selection + handles
│   ├── HistoryManager.cs      ← Undo/redo
│   └── ShapeCache.cs          ← Performance caching
├── Shapes/                    ← 8 shape renderers
├── Store/                     ← Reactive record store
└── Tools/                     ← 8 tool implementations

Tldraw.Blazor.Skia/           ← SkiaSharp Blazor component
└── TldrawCanvas.razor         ← Canvas with touch support

Tldraw.Blazor.App/            ← Demo app
├── Components/                ← UI panels
└── Pages/Home.razor           ← Full demo" />

    <h2 id="data-flow">
        Data Flow
        <a class="docs-anchor" href="#data-flow">#</a>
    </h2>

    <CodeBlock Language="text" Code="User Input → TldrawCanvas → Editor → ActiveTool → StateNode
                                                      ↓
                                               Store.Put/Remove
                                                      ↓
                                               Store.Changed event
                                                      ↓
                                               Editor.Invalidate()
                                                      ↓
                                               Render() → SKCanvas" />

    <h2 id="state-machine">
        Tool State Machine
        <a class="docs-anchor" href="#state-machine">#</a>
    </h2>
    <p>All tools use hierarchical <code>StateNode</code> state machines with transitions.</p>

    <CodeBlock Language="text" Code="SelectTool
├── IdleState
│   └── OnPointerDown → PointingState | BrushState | ArrowEditingState
├── PointingState
│   └── OnPointerMove (threshold) → DraggingState
├── DraggingState
│   └── OnPointerUp → IdleState
├── BrushState
│   └── OnPointerUp → IdleState
├── ResizingState
│   └── OnPointerUp → IdleState
├── RotatingState
│   └── OnPointerUp → IdleState
└── ArrowEditingState
    └── OnPointerUp → IdleState" />
</div>
